Calculated Insights List View

After creating a calculated insight in Data Cloud, see the details and edit your record from the Calculated Insights list view. The status, last run time, last run status, and schedule fields are updated in near-real time.

Use the dropdown arrow next to the calculated insight to change its content or status.

FUNCTION	PURPOSE
Edit	Change the calculated insight name and field names.
Clone	Duplicate and edit the SQL function from this record.
Enable/Disable	Turn processing on or off for a calculated insight.
Show in Builder	View calculated insight logic in the builder. Available only for calculated insights created with the builder.
Delete	Permanently remove a calculated insight and its connections.
Update Stats	Update the status, last run time, last run status, and last modified date of the selected calculated insight.
Publish Now	Run a calculated insight immediately instead of processing it as a batch schedule.
Schedule	Modify the processing schedule of a calculated insight.
